{"type":"message","id":"9b74424c","parentId":"3ee7e7a8","timestamp":"2026-03-09T11:39:24.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"下载下来的是 HTML 页面而不是图片。让我尝试找一下王者荣耀官方的图片 CDN URL。通常腾讯的图片会放在特定的 CDN 上。\n\n让我尝试从腾讯的 CDN 直接下载图片。王者荣耀的英雄图片通常在 pvp.qq.com 或者 game.qq.com 的 CDN 上。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4be8d1433d2940db8d2bed01","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace/images && curl -L -o dolya_1.jpg \"https://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/skin/hero-info/113/hero-info-113-big.jpg\" 2>&1 && file dolya_1.jpg && ls -la dolya_1.jpg","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773056361355}}
