{"type":"message","id":"cd2695ff","parentId":"f3e44b82","timestamp":"2026-03-09T11:40:05.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"萌娘百科访问失败了。让我尝试另一种方法 - 使用 Bing 图片搜索或者 Google 图片搜索的 API。\n\n实际上，让我尝试使用一个简单的 Python 脚本来搜索和下载图片，或者使用现有的 image_search.py 脚本但修复它的问题。\n\n让我先检查一下 image_search.py 的问题，看看能否修复它。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_99910c1c76e64205a8bbc690","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"path":"/usr/local/bin/image_search.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773056402504}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6d5dccf","parentId":"cd2695ff","timestamp":"2026-03-09T11:40:05.564Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_99910c1c76e64205a8bbc690","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nimage_search.py - 可靠的图片搜索和下载工具\n支持从 Bing 图片搜索下载高质量图片，带验证和重试机制。\n\n用法:\n  python3 /usr/local/bin/image_search.py \"搜索关键词\" [--limit 3] [--output /path/to/dir] [--min-size 10240]\n\"\"\"\n\nimport argparse\nimport hashlib\nimport json\nimport os\nimport re\nimport struct\nimport sys\nimport time\nimport urllib.parse\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nimport httpx\nfrom bs4 import BeautifulSoup\n\n\n# ─── 图片格式验证 ─────────────────────────────────────────────\nIMAGE_SIGNATURES = {\n    b'\\xff\\xd8\\xff': 'jpg',\n    b'\\x89PNG\\r\\n\\x1a\\n': 'png',\n    b'GIF87a': 'gif',\n    b'GIF89a': 'gif',\n    b'RIFF': 'webp',  # WebP starts with RIFF....WEBP\n    b'BM': 'bmp',\n}\n\ndef detect_image_format(data: bytes) -> str | None:\n    \"\"\"通过文件头检测图片格式\"\"\"\n    if len(data) < 12:\n        return None\n    for sig, fmt in IMAGE_SIGNATURES.items():\n        if data[:len(sig)] == sig:\n            if fmt == 'webp':\n                # WebP 需要额外检查 WEBP 标记\n                if data[8:12] == b'WEBP':\n                    return 'webp'\n                continue\n            return fmt\n    return None\n\n\ndef get_image_dimensions(data: bytes, fmt: str) -> tuple[int, int] | None:\n\n[340 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773056405555}}
